# {{name}} (Express + TypeScript)

## Scripts
- `pnpm dev` — start with hot-reload (tsx)
- `pnpm build` — compile TypeScript
- `pnpm start` — run compiled server
- `pnpm typecheck` — types only
- `pnpm test` — vitest (with supertest available)

## Endpoints
- `GET /healthz` — health check

## Auth
- Use `requireAuth` and `requireRole('admin')` middleware for protected routes.
- Tokens are **issued by your existing auth service**; this API only **verifies** JWTs and enforces roles.

## Env
- `PORT` (default: {{port}})
- `HOST` (default: 0.0.0.0)
- `JWT_SECRET` (required){{#if withDb}}
- `DATABASE_URL` (required for --db){{/if}}

## Docs
- Swagger UI at `/docs`

## Security
- helmet, CORS (open by default), express-rate-limit, cookie-parser

## Logging
- winston with simple request log middleware
